summary:
HEY @taylorswift ! 
A little life update ! I’m at my grandma’s place rn and today was such a beautiful day. Life was really...
body:
HEY @taylorswift !

A little life update ! I’m at my grandma’s place rn and today was such a beautiful day. Life was really difficult the past year but this year was finally the one I attended one of your shows !

It was everything I ever ever wanted

We were even twins !

I flew all the way from my tropical island and I started saving for your next tour so I’ll be sure ill be able to attend and see all my friends that I made this time around.

Attending one of your shows was the most healing experience I could ever hope for, fulfilling one of my craziest dreams was truly truly everything I ever wanted and I am so grateful that me the little island girl that had every album super late bc I live in the middle of nowhere, I was in that stadium with you.

Thank you for everything

I love you so much. @taylorswift @taylornation
